privateJob.title: Vodafoneidea Notification 2021 – Opening for Various Technical Executive Posts
privateJob.body:
Name of the post:

  • AGM – Technical Service Manager 

Description:

Vodafoneidea has issued a notification to fill the vacancies of various posts of AGM – Technical Service Manager. If you are finding jobs in Bangalore then feel free to apply online from The ProGrad .The candidates who are interested in the vacancies issued by Vodafoneidea can see the detailed information about key skills required, educational qualification, total vacancies, how to apply, roles and responsibilities are given below. Vodafoneidea is dealing with Telecom. If you are interested then read the details that are given below.

Total vacancies:

  • Various vacancies have released.

Selection Process:

  • Personal Interview

Role and responsibility:

Technical knowhow of Data & Voice Network: -

  • Should be able to understand the architecture of the services being offered under Wireline business •
  • Network audit for data links for any single point of failure and plan for additional resiliency.

Customer Focus: -

  • Handling customer faults and ensuring periodic communication to the customer during any outages
  • To ensure services offered to customer meet the agreed SLA with minimum MTTR •
  • Should be able to drive technical service improvement plan for services where SLA is not meeting.
  • Be part of MSA /SLA discussion with customers and signup process.

 These are some of the roles and responsibilities for one post. You should check for each post shown in applying now link

Application fee:

  • No information is given about the application required.

Educational qualification:

The candidates who are interested to apply for the Vodafoneidea job must have the following qualification:

  • The candidates must have completed the Engineering from a recognized university to apply for the application Vodafoneidea Notification 2021

Key skills required :

The candidates who are interested to apply in these job openings must have the following key skills that are required to do this:

  • Relevant experience handling Enterprise Customers 
  • Technical knowhow of Data & Voice Network
  • CCNA/CCNP preferred ITIL will be added advantage
  • Check it out on apply now link shown above for more skills.

Payscale info. :

  • The Payscale information will be decided at the time of the interview.

The document needs to be carried:

The candidates who will be selected for the interview must carry the below-mentioned documents:

  • The first and foremost thing is your resume/CV which has your educational background and other related information.
  • You must have your Adhaar card for identity purposes.
  • You must have other identity proofs like a PAN card, voter id, or Passport to prove your citizenship.
  • At last, you should have photocopies of important educational certificates.

How to apply for Vodafoneidea Notification 2021?

Candidates who are eligible and interested to apply for company Job then you should follow the below steps to apply:

  • Note: You can also apply by clicking the apply now button shown above to apply directly from here
  • First of all, read the Vodafoneidea Notification 2021 notification thoroughly at the official website @vodafoneidea.com.
  • You should have an email id and a phone number for communication purposes.
  • Click on the apply now link for the post you want to apply for.
  • Fill in the required details and submit.
  • Pay the application fee asked for.
  • Finally submit and download the application form for future purposes.
